HEADWORD: Vegete
<hw>Ve*gete"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>vegetus</ets>. See <er>Vegetable</er>.]</ety> <def>Lively; active;
sprightly; vigorous.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

